  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_5_2370-2408",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2370-2408",
      "markText": "但他不会生气，他会在自己和妻子的这些怒火之间，放置一道柔软但无法穿透的毯子。",
      "totalCount": 578,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2370&rangeEnd=2408",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2370&rangeEnd=2408"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_4_1439-1510",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1439-1510",
      "markText": "世界的洪流向他涌来，从来都不是空手而来，但他逐渐感觉到，他需要抵挡这些洪流，如果可能的话，他想改变水流的方向，修建堤坝，来抵挡生活前进的脚步。",
      "totalCount": 532,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1439&rangeEnd=1510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1439&rangeEnd=1510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_5_2295-2329",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2295-2329",
      "markText": "他觉得烦躁和痛苦都没有必要，那是灵魂反酸的时刻，需要用教养压制下去。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2295&rangeEnd=2329",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2295&rangeEnd=2329"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_7_1104-1134",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1104-1134",
      "markText": "现在，世界这条狗已经咬不到他了，而是和他一起奔跑，一起玩耍。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1104&rangeEnd=1134",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1104&rangeEnd=1134"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_4_454-523",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "454-523",
      "markText": "清晨的金属扶手很光滑，凉凉的，还没有被乘客汗津津的手捂热，摸上去很舒服。为了让那种感觉多停留几秒，他下车时慢吞吞的，并不是因为他行动不便。",
      "totalCount": 308,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=454&rangeEnd=523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=454&rangeEnd=523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_5_1844-1919",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1844-1919",
      "markText": "安娜已经去世很久了，在她去世之后，一切都变得模糊，他清楚记得他们的爱情，包括很多很小的细节，但那好像不是发生在他身上，而是可以发生在任何人身上的事情。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1844&rangeEnd=1919",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1844&rangeEnd=1919"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_5_2563-2596",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2563-2596",
      "markText": "自己之外的人——即使是最爱的人——也总是太多了，会让事情变得复杂。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2563&rangeEnd=2596",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2563&rangeEnd=2596"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_4_2349-2381",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2349-2381",
      "markText": "她不应该总是想着更换窗帘或吊灯，一旦开始改变，后面就很难预料了。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2349&rangeEnd=2381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2349&rangeEnd=2381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_13_3801-3886",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3801-3886",
      "markText": "在落下的叶子里有温暖过它的太阳，有通过雨点滋润过它的云朵，还有滋养过它的土地；叶子死去，它会把收到的东西还回去，这些组成了它的元素会继续存在。永远无常，是每样事物的永恒。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3801&rangeEnd=3886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3801&rangeEnd=3886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_5_766-798",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "766-798",
      "markText": "每逢赶路的时候，他都会早早起床，黑暗让睡眠带来的幸福感得以延续。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=766&rangeEnd=798",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=766&rangeEnd=798"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_4_2072-2117",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2072-2117",
      "markText": "就像他一直都觉得刷牙没什么用，消耗了那么多牙膏，牙医还是会赚很多钱，可他还是一直坚持刷牙。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2072&rangeEnd=2117",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2072&rangeEnd=2117"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071288_7_527-591",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "527-591",
      "markText": "他已经不在意时间了，有时候，他会把月份和星期搞混，就像有些早晨，由于一晚上没怎么睡好，醒来后不知道自己睡了几分钟，还是几个小时。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071288&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=527&rangeEnd=591",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/071324d0813ab8258g0189fb?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=527&rangeEnd=591"
    },
